{"type": "article", "id": 15175, "title": "T.O泡茶机", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-21T07:39:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115213D6ZewcArRaL7QiOf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t将袋装的速溶茶推广至全球的立顿和来自法国的 5.5 设计工作室合作开发一款泡茶机，将泡茶的繁琐步骤都仍给机器。放入茶叶加上水，由系统控制水温好茶叶量，剩下的时间就是等待一杯茶的诞生。水槽内带有 brita 净水器，让水保持更适合泡茶的中性。这款泡茶机有白色，红色，绿色和黑色四种金属机身，分别代表了不同颜色的茶。<a href=\"http://www.5-5designstudio.com/fr/projet/2015-to-by-lipton\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142446qxryt6TI81SQXGoZ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"282\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.34474328\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142447OyJFSmscG0IbQCkh.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261424474OmZn1u0hXafgKTt.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"589\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7200489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142447SV4jLHQCcZ5mexI7.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"614\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}